summary: This document is a draft search warrant affidavit prepared by an Assistant United States Attorney in the Southern District of New York, concerning a premises in New Hampshire. It appears to be part of the ongoing investigation into Jeffrey Epstein's activities.

persons.name: Assistant United States Attorney
persons.context: The author of the draft search warrant affidavit, working in the Southern District of New York.

keyFacts: A search warrant affidavit was being drafted for a premises in New Hampshire as part of the Epstein investigation.
The document was prepared by an Assistant United States Attorney from the Southern District of New York on July 2, 2020.
The document is a draft, indicating ongoing investigative activity.
